 cats. Available in multiple heights from 50 to 92 inches.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePros:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBudget-friendly (-150)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePressboard construction (stronger than cardboard)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMultiple color options\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e3. Vesper Cat Furniture Box - Modern Design\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you want something that looks good in your living room, Vesper\u0027s solid wood designs are both beautiful and sturdy enough for large cats.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e4. Armarkat Cat Tree - Most Stable\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eKnown for exceptional stability, Armarkat trees feature extra-wide bases and can be wall-anchored for maximum safety.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePros:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUp to 28-inch wide base\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWall-mounting hardware included\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReplaceable parts available\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e5. Molly and Friends Cat Tree - Handmade Quality\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHandcrafted in the USA from solid wood and quality carpet. These trees are built to last decades, not months.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSafety Tips for Large Cats\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlways check weight limits before purchasing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace the tree in a corner for added stability\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eConsider wall-mounting for very active cats\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInspect regularly for loose parts or wobbly sections\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTighten all screws during assembly\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSize Guide by Cat Weight\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e10-15 lbs:\u003c/strong\u003e Standard cat trees with 20-inch+ base\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e15-20 lbs:\u003c/strong\u003e Look for 24-inch+ base and 4-inch posts\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e20+ lbs:\u003c/strong\u003e Prioritize wall-mountable trees with solid wood construction\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eConclusion\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor large cats, the \u003cstrong\u003eFeandrea Cat Tree Tower\u003c/strong\u003e offers the best balance of stability and value. If you want something that will last forever, \u003cstrong\u003eMolly and Friends\u003c/strong\u003e handmade trees are worth the investment. Always prioritize a wide base and thick posts over height and features.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eAffiliate Disclosure: This article contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"
