        "content":  "\u003ch2\u003eWhy the Right Litter Box Matters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA good litter box keeps your home clean and your cat happy. The wrong one can lead to messes, odors, and even behavioral issues where your cat refuses to use it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003eWhat to Look For\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize:\u003c/strong\u003e Should be 1.5x your cat\u0027s length\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDepth:\u003c/strong\u003e Enough for 2-3 inches of litter\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEntry:\u003c/strong\u003e Low enough for easy access\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCovered vs Open:\u003c/strong\u003e Depends on your cat\u0027s preference\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eTop 5 Cat Litter Boxes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e1. Litter-Robot 4 - Best Automatic\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelf-cleaning litter box that sifts waste automatically. Expensive but saves time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePros:\u003c/strong\u003e Automatic cleaning, odor control, app connectivity\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCons:\u003c/strong\u003e Expensive (+), needs power outlet\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e2. Petmate Giant Litter Pan - Best Value\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExtra-large open pan at an affordable price. Simple but effective.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePros:\u003c/strong\u003e Large size, affordable (-25), easy to clean\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e3. Modkat Flip Litter Box - Best Covered\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eModern design with flip-top lid. Includes scoop and reusable liner.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePros:\u003c/strong\u003e Stylish, reduces tracking, easy to fill\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e4. Nature\u0027s Miracle High-Sided - Best for Kickers\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHigh sides prevent litter scatter. Non-stick surface for easy cleaning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e5. Catit Jumbo Hooded - Best for Large Cats\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExtra-large hooded box perfect for Maine Coons and other big breeds.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eTips for Success\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOne box per cat, plus one extra\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace in quiet, accessible location\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eScoop daily, deep clean weekly\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReplace box every 1-2 years (plastic absorbs odors)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eConclusion\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor most cats, the \u003cstrong\u003ePetmate Giant Litter Pan\u003c/strong\u003e offers the best value. For automatic cleaning, the \u003cstrong\u003eLitter-Robot 4\u003c/strong\u003e is worth the investment. Always choose a size larger than you think you need.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eAffiliate Disclosure: This article contains affiliate links.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"
